                  <summary><p>A collection of four works, the first three in Sanskrit and the last one in Telugu:
  <list rend="numbered">
    <item>Gaṇāṣṭaka</item>
    <item>Rāmāṣṭaka</item>
    <item>Bālakāṇḍa of the Rāmāyaṇa</item>
    <item>Letter in Telugu by Pōṭāru Sōmayya to his brother Pamiḍiceṭṭi Jaggayya about agricultural business</item>
    </list>
</p>
<p>See detailed description in Colas and Colas-Chauhan (1995, no. 53, pp. <ref target="https://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k2557038/f92">93</ref>-94).</p>
